White's descending move at 1 is the vital point of the capturing race. Anytime Black played here, the situation wasn't really good for White.
So as the famous proverb says, the opponent's vital point is my vital point.

The sequence from Black 2 to White 5 is the \cf1\b proof of White's win\cf0\b0 .
